{"tid":1971664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"星總理夫人改「Errr」文向台致謝","createTime":"2020-04-14T05:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T06:26:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0ed13df710381f937c48efc8893fc5074e88a8","tid":1971664,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:30:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200414/BTPI576Q54EQNIJAWFPWYHHHSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200414%2FBTPI576Q54EQNIJAWFPWYHHHSM%2F&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B8%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=26442ce6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200414%2FBTPI576Q54EQNIJAWFPWYHHHSM%2F&h=d5161198\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200414/BTPI576Q54EQNIJAWFPWYHHHSM/</a><br />\n<br />\n星總理夫人改「Errr」文向台致謝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200414/large/1586793626_8e82.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200414%2Flarge%2F1586793626_8e82.gif&h=369cced9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新加坡總理夫人何晶近日轉載台灣捐贈口罩新聞時，附文「Errrr....」，網民猜測她對台捐口罩不領情，事件惹兩地網民論戰。何晶昨修改帖文（圖），態度180度轉變，向台灣表示謝意之餘，同時又說「至於錯誤？也原諒了啦」，並放上多個表情符號，意思耐人尋味。<br />\n<br />\n籲停網絡廝殺共抗疫<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：獅城港人戴口罩受盡歧視<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何晶更新facebook帖文，稱對台灣所做的一切表示感謝，對於每個伸出援手、盡力幫助的人心懷感激。她又指，無論協助是否成功，誠心的努力與心意，她永遠珍惜。何也指，她要擁抱大家，停止網絡世界廝殺，戰勝病毒。事緣何晶上周六在fb轉載台灣捐口罩給新加坡的報道，疑因新加坡科技工程有限公司（ST Engineering）在台的兩條生產線，因台灣禁口罩出口，被迫將生產線搬回新加坡，惹何不滿，留下「Errrr....」暗示對台事後捐口罩不滿。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中央流行疫情指揮中心公佈最新疫情，台灣昨新增五宗確診病例，全部是外地輸入，為三女兩男，四人是爆發集體感染的珊瑚公主號郵輪旅客，另有一人（393例）是長期旅居美國的60多歲婦人，上月29日咳嗽及腹瀉，本月11日返台時有症狀，昨確診，她與早前確診的384例是夫妻，同在美國接觸過武漢肺炎確診者。外界質疑，為何該婦人出現症狀仍能上機返台。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"a5e50f29e5435764adb53e504c999d047b828078","tid":1971664,"uid":7355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"台灣：「Errrrr...」"},{"pid":"1ddc8a6d3d4b6418152f1bdfe9bd78d3dade0d23","tid":1971664,"uid":160964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"台灣雪中送炭<br />\n高智慧表現<br />\n贏哂"},{"pid":"f30ff36f2bf025aea6fe91b852a10e82b4bd0672","tid":1971664,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"Errr...."},{"pid":"90c858d79da745e4628c4750acf4b2a2df55ef71","tid":1971664,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:36:01.000Z","msg":"已經衰咗啦, 兜完都知你唔想領情, 死去奶共啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c5ebaed9c8f8a778533b41ee66938901b2b4df","tid":1971664,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:37:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfdVRb1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfdVRb1.gif&h=760071c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7034ee5fbd877af5c51740350e2c5ca43ba8a508","tid":1971664,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T05:51:26.000Z","msg":"monkey errrr monkey thank you"},{"pid":"f6d8ff6c069ed19fc3f8f646dc3ef52429432cd0","tid":1971664,"uid":67065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T06:26:21.000Z","msg":"至於錯誤？也原諒了啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錯係邊<br />\n死都唔認錯喎"}]}